{"tid":2374723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國台辦回應蕭美琴獲邀赴典禮　重申反對美台官方往來","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T12:34:30.000Z","uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa216af9ca4f806bb496663f74ee2679d9b4147","tid":2374723,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"國台辦回應蕭美琴獲邀赴典禮 重申反對美台官方往來<br />\n2021-01-21 HKT 18:55<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1571643_1_L_20210121190817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1571643_1_L_20210121190817.jpg&h=4083de13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在北京，國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮重申，堅決反對美國與台灣，進行任何形式的官方往來。<br />\n<br />\n台北駐美代表蕭美琴早前稱，獲邀出席美國總統就職禮。朱鳳蓮就事件回應傳媒提問時說，中方敦促美方恪守一個中國原則，及中美三個聯合公報有關規定，妥善處理台灣問題。<br />\n<br />\n她說民進黨當局任何伎倆及藉口，都掩蓋不到台獨本性，又指民進黨當局必將自食惡果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571643-20210121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571643-20210121.htm&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=adfe226b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571643-20210121.htm&h=43989377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571643-20210121.htm</a>"},{"pid":"91e72f536b4710b30eff255d5c3b50c042852af4","tid":2374723,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:27:29.000Z","msg":"又干涉美國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba99919c8de7f4435d96fea270741e00c9309117","tid":2374723,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"7eda008cf1a0febea1ed7bcb1854d25a4b89579f","tid":2374723,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:34:30.000Z","msg":"內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}